{"tid":1203290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致仍然舉旗不定既朋友們","createTime":"2019-06-11T12:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:39:32.000Z","uid":43660,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae44657bf141523e6bcb5189bd997e7bd4244e6","tid":1203290,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"黎緊既48小時 注定會寫入歷史冊其中一章<br />\n你係咪仲擔心緊聽日罷工請假會被其他同事睇你唔起?<br />\n你係咪仲擔心緊聽日出黎會比人打到仆街?<br />\n係咪仲奢望緊政府會收回條例?<br />\n<br />\n好多香港人一向都好天真 包括我自己在內<br />\n覺得好多野等其他人去爭取 自己坐享其成<br />\n但係今次呢條條例一過 你又會唔會對得住黎緊既下一代?<br />\n希望以上呢番說話可以呼籲到更多人聽日到場為自己爭取<br />\n因為大家都熱愛呢片土地 大家都係香港人!<br />\n利申:中資公司假已請 各位聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508cc9c4b5767962f42374b27333611ceacbd014","tid":1203290,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0ff33f9a1be4d57d5c813436b9d670900025df8","tid":1203290,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e81787386acfcb2b50285ab70f73d19f7678c40","tid":1203290,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"816abeb59ea610f2d98054bd8031b885ff59e539","tid":1203290,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73ecf189c22ad1c30b8f3420a314f769e4a1b138","tid":1203290,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:24:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90f01130e85e651bbfcd107a2221e4ebb5fbf701","tid":1203290,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}